ZH: 我们每天午休的时间间隔为一个小时。
EN: The interval for our daily lunch break is one hour.

ZH: 每隔五分钟，火车就会到达一站。
EN: The train arrives at each station every five minutes.

ZH: 医生建议我每次服药的间隔为六小时。
EN: The doctor advised me to take the medication at six-hour intervals.

ZH: 这个工作需要你在每次完成任务后有一段时间的间隔。
EN: This job requires you to have a certain interval of time after completing each task.

ZH: 学生必须距离午餐时间开始前的那一段时间内交作业。
EN: Students must submit their assignments within a certain interval before lunchtime.

ZH: 她的微笑间隔了几秒，然后她开始讲话。
EN: There was a brief interval of a few seconds before she started speaking.

ZH: 这首歌的两个间奏之间有一个较长的间隔。
EN: There is a longer interval between the two interludes in this song.

ZH: 她每隔一段时间就会做一次瑜伽。
EN: She does yoga at intervals.

